data.description: Experience the epitome of St. Matthews living in this amazing Cape Cod home on a prestigious street. The spacious living room with a fireplace, upgraded kitchen with granite tops, and two bedrooms on the first floor create an inviting atmosphere. The second-floor master exudes luxury with a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, and a renovated master bathroom. Hardwood floors grace the first floor, while the finished basement, boasting new flooring, adds extra space with a family room, bar area, laundry room, and workshop/storage. The outdoor haven includes a covered front porch, back deck, privacy-fenced yard, and a patio with a fire pit on a private corner lot. Park effortlessly with a 2-car garage and 1-car carport. Walkable to groceries, restaurants, and gyms! Schedule your showing today!
